text:
Keep attacking Crocomire in its mouth to push him back until he falls.

Charge Beam+Ice Beam while Power Bomb is on select button.
Charge your beam normally and you get 4 ice shields that attack.
You can't attack while using it but you should somewhat be ok.
Charge Beam+Spazer while Power Bomb is on select gives you beams that spread out around you to attack your surrounding enemies.

Can't wait for you to fight against Phantoon. You'll have an extremely hard time, I suggest going out of your way and find more missiles and energy tanks.

Ridley's boss fight and lower norfair's awesome run with soundtrack are epic and memorable.

text: For those who want more Super Metroid experiences, try visiting the website called MetroidConstruction. There, people make their own hacks (custom versions of Super Metroid and other Metroids) in patch formats that you apply on your game file and some hacks are incredibly good and much longer than the original game. Some examples are Super Metroid Cliffhanger and Super Metroid Redesign, you can look for walkthroughs here on YT. Some are very hard, so be prepared. There are also complete maps on the internet in case you go for a 100% item collection.
